<div id="review_1905496057" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1905496057" />
    <a title="Janez" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/7296492-janez"><img alt="Janez" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1385306162p2/7296492.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1905496057?book_show_action=true">Feb 12, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Janez" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Janez" href="/user/show/7296492-janez">Janez</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780140621839" href="/book/show/77994.Selected_Short_Stories">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7296492-janez?shelf=fiction">fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7296492-janez?shelf=library-books">library-books</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7296492-janez?shelf=classics">classics</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7296492-janez?shelf=france">france</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7296492-janez?shelf=favorites">favorites</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/7296492-janez?shelf=short-stories">short-stories</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1905496057" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12283905788047539261">Whether describing the horrors of the Franco-Prussian war, vignettes of the times long gone, deadly Corsican vendetta, avarice, humorous situations or the prostitues bringing to tears the whole religious community, Maupassant never disappoints. His style is light, vivacious and his descriptions of the nature, especially of his beloved Normandy, give the reader a feeling to be present at the spot. Maupassant is quickly becoming one of my favourite authors!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


