        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2765046252" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15755424270741921103">I am late to writing this review as I was away when I finished this collection. I will say that the stories seemed to be good but hampered by a very unfortunate translation that was made even more difficult to enjoy by the faulty transcription to the ebook version that I read. I think this was an interesting collection of stories from a writer from this period and I think that there is a spark of something more in these tales and I&apos;m disappointed that it was lost in the translation. Don&apos;t take m</span>
  <span id="freeText15755424270741921103" style="display:none">I am late to writing this review as I was away when I finished this collection. I will say that the stories seemed to be good but hampered by a very unfortunate translation that was made even more difficult to enjoy by the faulty transcription to the ebook version that I read. I think this was an interesting collection of stories from a writer from this period and I think that there is a spark of something more in these tales and I'm disappointed that it was lost in the translation. Don't take my three stars as a critique of the writing because it was good and the stories, while a bit on the paltry side of things, I believe are less the fault of the author and more of the edition that I got saddled with. De Maupassant still deserves your attention and you should look up more, but buyer beware of your editions.</span>
  <a data-text-id="15755424270741921103" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
