        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3525739386" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13515705141102810899">I like short stories, especially those with a twist or a great ending. This author prefers slice of life stories that often end abruptly. He writes well, and illuminates characters quickly, but rarely develops toward a satisfying conclusion.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


